msgstr "State"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1943
msgid "Defines the state of a process. Possible values:"
msgstr "Задает состояние процесса. Возможные значения:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1947
msgid "'Active' are all processes which can be used in new process tickets."
msgstr ""
"'Active' / Активный - все процессы, которые могут быть использованы в новых "
"процессных заявках."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1952
msgid ""
"'FadeAway' are processes which cannot be selected any more for new tickets, "
"but existing tickets still can use the process."
msgstr ""
"'FadeAway' / Исчезающие - это процессы, которые нельзя выбрать более для "
"новых заявок, но существующие заявки могут продолжать их использовать."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1958
msgid ""
"'Inactive' processes are deactivated and cannot be used for new or existing "
"tickets."
msgstr ""
"'Inactive' / Неактивные - деактивированные процессы. Они не могут быть более "
"использованы ни в новых, ни в существующих заявках."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1966
msgid "StartActivity"
msgstr "StartActivity"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1968
msgid ""
"When creating a new process ticket, a StartActivity must be defined. As soon "
"as the ticket is created, this Activity will be set and used as the base for "
"the first transition checks."
msgstr ""
"При создании новой процессной заявки, StartActivity / Начальная Активность "
"должна быть задана.Как только заявка будет создана, эта Активность будет "
"инициирована и использована как начальная точка для первых проверок "
"переходов."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1974
msgid "StartActivityDialog"
msgstr "StartActivityDialog"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1976
msgid ""
"For new process tickets, a StartActivityDialog must be defined. This will be "
"shown when creating a new process ticket (after the process was selected). "
"At this point, the ticket does not exist yet, it will be created after "
"submitting the StartActivityDialog."
msgstr ""
"Для новой процессной заявки должен быть задан StartActivityDialog/Начальный "
"Диалог Активности. Он будет показан при создании новой процессной заявки "
"(после выбора процесс). В этот момент заявка еще не существует, она будет "
"создана после выполнения StartActivityDialog."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1983
msgid "Path"
msgstr "Путь"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1985
msgid ""
"The Path contains the structure of the Activities, and the possible "
"Transitions between them, for the current process. And also the Transition "
"Actions that happens when transitioning . This controls the way that a "
"process ticket can take. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Схема отображает структуру Активностей и возможных Переходов между ними для "
"текущего процесса. А также Действия Переходов/Transition Actions возможные "
"при переходах. Она показывает пути выполнения процессной заявки. Например:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:1992
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"'A1' => {\n"
"    'T1' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A2',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T2' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A3',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T3' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A4',\n"
"        TransitionAction => ['TA1', 'TA2'],\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"'A1' => {\n"
"    'T1' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A2',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T2' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A3',\n"
"    },\n"
"    'T3' => {\n"
"        ActivityEntityID => 'A4',\n"
"        TransitionAction => ['TA1', 'TA2'],\n"
"    },\n"
"},\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2007
msgid ""
"If a process ticket is in Activity 'A1', it has three possible ways to get "
"to another Activity. In the Transitions 'T1' to 'T3', conditions are "
"defined, that a process ticket must fulfill to move (transit) to another "
"Activity."
msgstr ""
"Если процессная заявка в состоянии Activity 'A1', она имеет три возможных "
"пути перехода к другой Активности. Для Переходов от 'T1' до 'T3' заданы "
"условия, которые процессная заявка должна выполнить для перехода (transit) к "
"следующей Активности."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2012
msgid ""
"If in this case all the values of the process ticket and its dynamic fields "
"that are needed for the Transition 'T2' are correct, the ticket will be "
"moved from Activity 'A1' to 'A3'. After an ActivityDialog is submitted, or "
"any other change is made to a ticket, it will be checked for possible "
"Transitions from the current Activity. If multiple Transitions are possible, "
"the first one will be used (based on numerical sorting of the TransitionIDs)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2020
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is possible to assign Transition Actions to Transitions in "
"the Path configuration. These are modules which are executed after a "
"successful Transition. They have to be specified in array form as in the "
"example, we'll talk about the details later."
msgstr ""
"Дополнительно, имеется возможность назначить Действия Переходов при "
"конфигурации Процесса. Это модули, которые будут выполняться после успешного "
"Перехода. Они должны быть заданы в виде массива/таблицы, как в примере, "
"подробности этого мы обсудим позже."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2029
msgid "Activity"
msgstr "Активность"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2031
msgid ""
"An Activity contains one or more Activity Dialogs and models a 'step' in the "
"process. All Activity Dialogs of the current Activity are displayed in the "
"ticket zoom and can be used until the conditions of a Transition are "
"fulfilled."
msgstr ""
"Активность содержит один или более Диалог Активности и представляет собой "
"этап Процесса. Все Диалоги Активности отображаются на экране подробного "
"просмотра заявки TicketZoom и используются, пока условия Перехода "
"выполняются."

