#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3033
msgid "'Subject' defines the article title. Mandatory."
msgstr "Тема - задает заголовок сообщения/заметки. Обязательна."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2843
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3036
msgid "'Body' defines the article content. Mandatory."
msgstr "\"Тело\" - задает содержимое сообщения/заметки. Указывать обязательно."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2846
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3039
msgid ""
"'HistoryType' defines the type of the history entry. Possible values: "
"AddNote, ArchiveFlagUpdate, Bounce, CustomerUpdate, EmailAgent, "
"EmailCustomer, EscalationResponseTimeNotifyBefore, "
"EscalationResponseTimeStart, EscalationResponseTimeStop, "
"EscalationSolutionTimeNotifyBefore, EscalationSolutionTimeStart, "
"EscalationSolutionTimeStop, EscalationUpdateTimeNotifyBefore, "
"EscalationUpdateTimeStart, EscalationUpdateTimeStop, FollowUp, Forward, "
"Lock, LoopProtection, Merged, Misc, Move, NewTicket, OwnerUpdate, "
"PhoneCallAgent, PhoneCallCustomer, PriorityUpdate, Remove, "
"ResponsibleUpdate, SendAgentNotification, SendAnswer, SendAutoFollowUp, "
"SendAutoReject, SendAutoReply, SendCustomerNotification, ServiceUpdate, "
"SetPendingTime, SLAUpdate, StateUpdate, Subscribe, SystemRequest, "
"TicketDynamicFieldUpdate, TicketLinkAdd, TicketLinkDelete, TimeAccounting, "
"TypeUpdate, Unlock, Unsubscribe, WebRequestCustomer."
msgstr ""
"'HistoryType/Тип записи Истории' задает типы/названия записей истории "
"заявки.  Возможные значения: AddNote, ArchiveFlagUpdate, Bounce, "
"CustomerUpdate, EmailAgent, EmailCustomer, "
"EscalationResponseTimeNotifyBefore, EscalationResponseTimeStart, "
"EscalationResponseTimeStop, EscalationSolutionTimeNotifyBefore, "
"EscalationSolutionTimeStart, EscalationSolutionTimeStop, "
"EscalationUpdateTimeNotifyBefore, EscalationUpdateTimeStart, "
"EscalationUpdateTimeStop, FollowUp, Forward, Lock, LoopProtection, Merged, "
"Misc, Move, NewTicket, OwnerUpdate, PhoneCallAgent, PhoneCallCustomer, "
"PriorityUpdate, Remove, ResponsibleUpdate, SendAgentNotification, "
"SendAnswer, SendAutoFollowUp, SendAutoReject, SendAutoReply, "
"SendCustomerNotification, ServiceUpdate, SetPendingTime, SLAUpdate, "
"StateUpdate, Subscribe, SystemRequest, TicketDynamicFieldUpdate, "
"TicketLinkAdd, TicketLinkDelete, TimeAccounting, TypeUpdate, Unlock, "
"Unsubscribe, WebRequestCustomer."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2862
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3055
msgid "'HistoryComment' defines the content of the history entry."
msgstr "\"HistoryComment\" описывает содержимое записи истории."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2865
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3058
msgid ""
"'From', 'To', 'Cc' and 'ReplyTo' take email addresses in the notation "
"specified above."
msgstr ""
"\"От\", \"Кому\", \"Копия\" и \"Ответить\" задает адреса электронной почты с "
"учетом правил, указанных выше."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2869
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3062
msgid "'InReplyTo' and 'References' take email message IDs."
msgstr "'InReplyTo' и 'References' получает идентификаторы/IDs сообщений."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2872
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3065
msgid ""
"'NoAgentNotify' - if set to 1, the email notification of the Agent will not "
"be sent."
msgstr ""
"\"NoAgentNotify\"/Не иформировать агента - если установлено в \"1\", "
"уведомление агенту посылаться не будет."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2876
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3069
msgid ""
"'AutoResponseType' can take the following values: auto follow up, auto "
"reject, auto remove, auto reply, auto reply/new ticket."
msgstr ""
"\"AutoResponseType\"/\"Тип автоответа\" - может принимать следующие "
"значения:  auto follow up/автоотклик, auto reject/автоотказ, auto remove/"
"автоудаление, auto reply/автоответ, auto reply/new ticket/автоответ-новая "
"заявка."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2880
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3073
msgid ""
"'ForceNotificationToUserID', 'ExcludeNotificationToUserID', "
"'ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID' can take a list of UserIDs that are either "
"always notified, not notified or listed as notified but not actually sent a "
"notification email."
msgstr ""
"'ForceNotificationToUserID', 'ExcludeNotificationToUserID', "
"'ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID' может содержать список UserIDs, которые "
"либо всегда оповешаются, не оповещаются, либо  помечаются как оповещенные, "
"но на самом деле им не отправлено уведомление по электронной почте."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2889
msgid ""
"Creates a ticket with an article, the new ticket can be linked with process "
"ticket. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Создает заявку с сообщением, новая заявка может быть связана с процессной "
"заявкой. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2893
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Ticket Create',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketCreate',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"\n"
"            # ticket required:\n"
"            Title         => 'Some Ticket Title',\n"
"            Queue         => 'Raw',              # or QueueID => 123,\n"
"            Lock          => 'unlock',\n"
"            Priority      => '3 normal',         # or PriorityID => 2,\n"
"            State         => 'new',              # or StateID => 5,\n"
"            CustomerID    => '123465',\n"
"            CustomerUser  => 'customer@example.com',\n"
"            OwnerID       => 123,\n"
"\n"
"            # ticket optional:\n"
"            TN              => $TicketObject->TicketCreateNumber(), # optional\n"
"            Type            => 'Incident',            # or TypeID => 1, not required\n"
"            Service         => 'Service A',           # or ServiceID => 1, not required\n"
"            SLA             => 'SLA A',               # or SLAID => 1, not required\n"
"            ResponsibleID   => 123,                   # not required\n"
"            ArchiveFlag     => 'y',                   # (y|n) not required\n"
"            PendingTime     => '2011-12-23 23:05:00', # optional (for pending states)\n"
"            PendingTimeDiff => 123 ,                  # optional (for pending states)\n"
"\n"
"            # article required:\n"
"            ArticleType      => 'note-internal',                        # note-external|phone|fax|sms|...\n"
"                                                                        #   excluding any email type\n"
"            SenderType       => 'agent',                                # agent|system|customer\n"
"            ContentType      => 'text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-15',      # or optional Charset & MimeType\n"
"            Subject          => 'some short description',               # required\n"
"            Body             => 'the message text',                     # required\n"
"            HistoryType      => 'OwnerUpdate',                          #\n"
"            EmailCustomer|Move|AddNote|PriorityUpdate|WebRequestCustomer|...\n"
"            HistoryComment   => 'Some free text!',\n"
"\n"
"            # article optional:\n"
"            From             => 'Some Agent <email@example.com>',       # not required but useful\n"
"            To               => 'Some Customer A <customer-a@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            Cc               => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            ReplyTo          => 'Some Customer B <customer-b@example.com>', # not required\n"
"            MessageID        => '<asdasdasd.123@example.com>',          # not required but useful\n"
"            InReplyTo        => '<asdasdasd.12@example.com>',           # not required but useful\n"
"            References       => '<asdasdasd.1@example.com> <asdasdasd.12@example.com>', # not required but useful\n"
"            NoAgentNotify    => 0,                                      # if you don't want to send agent notifications\n"
"            AutoResponseType => 'auto reply'                            # auto reject|auto follow up|auto reply/new ticket|auto remove\n"
"\n"
"            ForceNotificationToUserID   => [ 1, 43, 56 ],               # if you want to force somebody\n"
"            ExcludeNotificationToUserID => [ 43,56 ],                   # if you want full exclude somebody from notifications,\n"
"                                                                        # will also be removed in To: line of article,\n"
"                                                                        # higher prio as ForceNotificationToUserID\n"
"            ExcludeMuteNotificationToUserID => [ 43,56 ],               # the same as ExcludeNotificationToUserID but only the\n"
"                                                                        # sending gets muted, agent will still shown in To:\n"
"                                                                        # line of article\n"
"            TimeUnit                        => 123\n"
"\n"
"            # other:\n"
"            DynamicField_NameX => $Value,\n"
"            LinkAs => $LinkType,                                        # Normal, Parent, Child, etc. (respective original ticket)\n"
"            UserID => 123,                                              # optional, to override the UserID from the logged user\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2965
msgid "'Title' The ticket title."
msgstr "'Название' Название заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2968
msgid ""
"'Queue' or 'QueueID' specifies the name or id of the queue to be used in the "
"new ticket."
msgstr ""
"'Queue' или 'QueueID' задает имя или идентификатор очереди для использования "
"в новой заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2972
msgid "'Lock' or 'LockID' sets the lock status of the ticket."
msgstr "'Lock' или 'LockID' задает статус блокировки для заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2975
msgid ""
"'Priority' or 'PriorityID' specifies the name or id of the priority to be "
"used in the new ticket."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2979
msgid ""
"'State' or 'StateID' specifies the name or id of the state to be used in the "
"new ticket."
msgstr ""
"'State' или 'StateID' задает состояние или его идентификатор для "
"использования в новой заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2983
msgid "'CustomerID', the customer id to be set for the new ticket."
msgstr ""
"'CustomerID', идентификатор клиента/компании клиента для указания в новой "
"заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2986
msgid ""
"'CustomerUser', the login of the customer that will be assigned in the "
"ticket."
msgstr "'CustomerUser', имя входа/login клиента, назначаемый новой заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2990
msgid "'OwnerID', the ID of the agent that will be the new ticket owner."
msgstr "'OwnerID', ID агента, который будет новым владельцем заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2993
msgid "'TN', custom number for the new ticket."
msgstr "'TN', пользовательский номер новой заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:2996
msgid ""
"'Type' or 'TypeID' specifies the name or id of the ticket type to be used in "
"the new ticket."
msgstr ""
"'Type' или 'TypeID' задает название или id типа заявки для использования в "
"новой заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3000
msgid ""
"'Service' or 'ServiceID' specifies the name or id of the service to be used "
"in the new ticket."
msgstr ""
"Service' или 'ServiceID' задает название или id Сервиса для использования в "
"новой заявке."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3004
msgid ""
"'SLA' or 'SLAID' specifies the name or id of the SLA to be used in the new "
"ticket."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3008
msgid ""
"'ResponsibleID', the ID of the agent that will be the new ticket responsible."
msgstr ""
"'ResponsibleID', ID агента, назначаемого ответственным за новую заявку."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3011
msgid ""
"'PendingTime', a predefined date to set the Ticket Pending Times, when the "
"ticket state belongs to a pending state type."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3015
msgid ""
"'PendingTimeDiff', a dynamically date (expressed in seconds from current "
"date/time) to set the Ticket Pending Times, when the ticket state belongs to "
"a pending state type."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3025
msgid ""
"SenderType defines the sender type of the article. Possible values: agent, "
"system, customer."
msgstr ""
"Тип отправителя задает тип отправителя для заметки/сообщения. Возможные "
"значения: агент, система, клиент."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3079
msgid ""
"'TimeUnit' the time invested in the current ticket article expressed in "
"seconds, minutes, hours, etc."
msgstr ""
"'TimeUnit/Единицы времени' - время, потраченное на текущее действие по "
"заявке, выраженное секундах, минутах, часах,  и т. д."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3083
msgid ""
"'DynamicField_NameX' where DynamicField_ is a required prefix and NameX is "
"the name of a Dynamic Field to be set in the new ticket (on ticket level, "
"not article levels)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3088
msgid ""
"'LinkAs' to define the new ticket relation with originator ticket, from the "
"new ticket point of view, for example Normal, Parent, Child etc."
msgstr ""
"'LinkAs/Связать как' для определения отношения к оригинальной заявке, с "
"точки зрения новой заявки, например, Normal/Обычная, Parent/Родитель, Child/"
"Потомок и т. д."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3095
msgid "Sets the customer of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Задает клиента процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3098
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Customer Set Customer to test',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::Process::TransitionAction::TicketCustomerSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            No      => 'test',\n"
"            User    => 'client-user-123',\n"
"            # or in other words\n"
"            # CustomerID     => 'client123',\n"
"            # CustomerUserID => 'client-user-123',\n"
"\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Customer Set Customer to test',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::Process::TransitionAction::TicketCustomerSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            No      => 'test',\n"
"            User    => 'client-user-123',\n"
"            # or in other words\n"
"            # CustomerID     => 'client123',\n"
"            # CustomerUserID => 'client-user-123',\n"
"\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3119
msgid "'No' or 'CustomerID' set the Customer ID of the customer."
msgstr "'No' или 'CustomerID' задает Customer ID клиента."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3122
msgid "'User' or 'CustomerUserID' set the Username of the customer."
msgstr "'User' или 'CustomerUserID' задает имя пользователя клиента."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3129
msgid "Changes the lock of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Устанавливает состояние блокирования процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3132
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Lock to lock',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketLockSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Lock   => 'lock',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            LockID => 2,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Lock to lock',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketLockSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Lock   => 'lock',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            LockID => 2,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3150
msgid "'Lock' defines the new lock of the process ticket."
msgstr ""
"'Lock/Блокировка' - задает новый статус блокировки для процессной заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3153
msgid "'LockID' defines the internal ID of the new lock."
msgstr "'LockID' задает внутренний ID нового статуса блокировки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3160
msgid "Changes the owner of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Изменяет владельца этой процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3163
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Owner Set root@localhost',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketOwnerSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Owner => 'root@localhost',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            OwnerID => 1,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Owner Set root@localhost',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketOwnerSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Owner => 'root@localhost',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            OwnerID => 1,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3181
msgid "'Owner' specifies the login name of the new owner."
msgstr "\"Owner\"/\"Владелец\" - задает логин нового владельца."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3184
msgid "'OwnerID' specifies the internal ID of the new owner."
msgstr "\"OwnerID\" задает внутренний ID нового владельца."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3191
msgid "Moves the ticket into a target queue. Example:"
msgstr "Перемещает заявку в указанную очередь. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3194
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move Raw',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue => 'Raw',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            # QueueID => '2',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Queue Move Raw',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketQueueSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Queue => 'Raw',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            # QueueID => '2',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3212
msgid "'Queue' specifies the name of the target queue."
msgstr "\"Queue\" задает имя очереди для перемещения."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3215
msgid "'QueueID' specifies the internal ID of the target queue."
msgstr "\"QueueID\" задает внутренний ID для очереди для перемещения."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3222
msgid "Changes the responsible of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Изменяет владельца процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3225
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Responsible Set root@localhost',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketResponsibleSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Responsible => 'root@localhost',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            ResponsibleID => 1,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Responsible Set root@localhost',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketResponsibleSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Responsible => 'root@localhost',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            ResponsibleID => 1,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3243
msgid "'Responsible' specifies the login name of the new responsible."
msgstr "\"Responsible\" задает логин нового ответственного."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3246
msgid "'ResponsibleID' specifies the internal ID of the new responsible."
msgstr "\"ResponsibleID\" задает внутренний ID нового ответственного."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3253
msgid ""
"Assigns a service to a process ticket.  The ticket requires to have a "
"customer and the service must be assigned to that customer.  Example:"
msgstr ""
"Назначает сервис процессной заявке. Заявка должна иметь клиента и сервис "
"должен быть назначен этому клиенту. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3259
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set MyService service',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketServiceSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Service   => 'MyService',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            ServiceID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set MyService service',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketServiceSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Service   => 'MyService',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            ServiceID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3277
msgid ""
"'Service' defines the new service of the process ticket. The full name is "
"required (e.g. GramdFatherService::FatherService::SonService )."
msgstr ""
"\"Service\" задает новый сервис для процессной заявки. Требуется задать "
"полное имя сервиса (например, GrandFatherService::FatherService::"
"SonService )."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3281
msgid "'ServiceID' defines the internal ID of the new service."
msgstr "\"ServiceID\" задает внутренний ID нового сервиса."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3288
msgid ""
"Assigns a service level agreement to a process ticket.  The ticket requires "
"to have a service and the SLA must be assigned to that service.  Example:"
msgstr ""
"Задает SLA для процессной заявки. Заявке должен быть уже назначен сервис и "
"SLA должен быть привязан к этому сервису. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3294
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set MySLA SLA',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketSLASet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            SLA   => 'MySLA',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            SLAID => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3312
msgid "'SLA' defines the new service level agreement of the process ticket."
msgstr ""
"\"SLA\" задает новое соглашение об уровне сервиса для процессной заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3315
msgid "'SLAID' defines the internal ID of the new SLA."
msgstr "\"SLAID\" задает внутренний ID новогоSLA."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3322
msgid "Changes the state of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Изменяет состояние процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3325
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set State to open',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketStateSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            State   => 'open',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            StateID => 4,\n"
"\n"
"            PendingTimeDiff => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set State to open',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketStateSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            State   => 'open',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            StateID => 4,\n"
"\n"
"            PendingTimeDiff => 123,\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3345
msgid "'State' defines the new state of the process ticket."
msgstr "\"State\" задает новое состояние процессной заявки. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3348
msgid "'StateID' defines the internal ID of the new state."
msgstr "\"StateID\" задает внутренний ID нового состояния."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3351
msgid ""
"'PendingTimeDiff' used only for pending type states, defines the time "
"difference in seconds relative (relative to the Transition Action execution "
"time) to set ticket pending time (e.g. 3600 means that the pending time is "
"1hr after the Transition Action is executed)."
msgstr ""
"\"PendingTimeDiff\" используется только для состояний с ожиданием, задает "
"относительную разность в секундах (относительно заданного времени выполнения "
"Действия Перехода) для установки времени ожидания для заявки (например, 3600 "
"означает что устанавливается ожидание в 1 час после заданного времени "
"выполнения Действия Перехода)."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3361
msgid "Sets the ticket title of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Задает Тему процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3364
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Ticket Title to Ticket-title',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketTitleSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Title => 'Ticket-title',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Ticket Title to Ticket-title',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketTitleSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Title => 'Ticket-title',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3380
msgid "'Title' specifies the new title of the ticket."
msgstr "\"Title\" задает новую тему заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3387
msgid "Sets the ticket type of a process ticket. Example:"
msgstr "Задает Тип процессной заявки. Пример:"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3390
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Ticket Type to default',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketTypeSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Type     => 'default',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            # TypeID => '1',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
msgstr ""
"$Self->{'Process::TransitionAction'} = {\n"
"    'TA1' => {\n"
"        Name   => 'Set Ticket Type to default',\n"
"        Module => 'Kernel::System::ProcessManagement::TransitionAction::TicketTypeSet',\n"
"        Config => {\n"
"            Type     => 'default',\n"
"            # or\n"
"            # TypeID => '1',\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3408
msgid "'Type' specifies the name of the ticket type."
msgstr "\"Type\"/\"Тип\" - задает название типа заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3411
msgid "'TypeID' specifies the internal ID of the ticket type."
msgstr "\"TypeID\" задает внутренний ID для типа заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3418
#: en/content/customization/acl.xml:5
msgid "Access Control Lists (ACLs)"
msgstr "Списки Контроля Доступа (ACLs)"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3420
msgid ""
"With the help of ACLs, you can limit selectable values in process tickets.  "
"Please also see the <link linkend=\"acl-reference\">ACL reference</link> for "
"a description of the full ticket ACL syntax."
msgstr ""
"С помощью ACL, вы можете ограничить выбор значений в процессной заявке. "
"Смотрите также <link linkend=\"acl-reference\">ACL reference</link> для "
"обзора полного синтаксиса ACL для заявок."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3425
msgid "ACL configuration"
msgstr "Настройка ACL"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3427
msgid ""
"ACLs can only be defined in <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>. Example:"
msgstr ""
"ACL могут быть заданы только в <filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename>. /"
"Правильнее с помощью редактора ACL в SysConfig/. Пример:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3431
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-ProcessProperties'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Process => {\n"
"            ProcessEntityID        => ['P1'],\n"
"            ActivityEntityID       => ['A1'],\n"
"            ActivityDialogEntityID => ['AD1'],\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3450
msgid "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"
msgstr "001-ACL-ProcessProperties"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3452
msgid ""
"Name of the ACL rule. For further information on ACL rules in general, "
"please consult <link linkend=\"acl\">the ACL manual</link>."
msgstr ""
"Имя правила ACL. Для более полной информации обратитесь к <link linkend=\"acl"
"\">the ACL manual</link>."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3459
msgid ""
"This is the section that is used to check if an ACL must be applied. If it "
"has the specified values, the rule is applied. The following values can be "
"used:"
msgstr ""
"Эта секция предназначена для проверки может ли правило ACL быть применено. "
"Если параметр имеет заданное значение, правило применяется. Могут быть "
"использованы следующие значения:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3463
msgid "ProcessEntityID"
msgstr "ProcessEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3465
msgid ""
"The ID of a process that the process. Matches if the ticket is assigned to "
"this process."
msgstr ""
"ID процесса для текущего процесса. Совпадает, если заявка назначена этому "
"процессу."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3470
msgid "ActivityEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3472
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity that the process ticket currently is assigned to."
msgstr "ID Активности, которой назначена процессная заявка в текущий момент."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3476
msgid "ActivityDialogEntityID"
msgstr "ActivityDialogEntityID"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3478
msgid ""
"The ID of the Activity Dialog that is currently open for a process ticket."
msgstr ""
"ID Диалога Активности открытого в настоящий момент для процессной заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3483
msgid "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog"
msgstr "Possible/PossibleNot Activity Dialog/Диалог Активности"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3485
msgid ""
"Here you can specify a list of Activity Dialog IDs. This list will limit the "
"possible Activity Dialogs that are offered to the user in the ticket zoom "
"mask."
msgstr ""
"Здесь вы можете задать список ID'ов Диалогов Активности. Этот список "
"ограничивает Диалоги Активности, которые могут быть предложены пользователю "
"при просмотре заявки."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3489
msgid ""
"'Possible' lists the Activity Dialogs that are allowed. The setting above "
"will only allow 'AD1' and 'AD3' of the list of configured Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"\"Possible\" показывает список допустимых Диалогов Активности. Установка "
"выше, допускает только 'AD1' и 'AD3' из списка заданных Диалогов Активности."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3493
msgid ""
"'PossibleNot' lists the Activity Dialogs that are not allowed. In the "
"example above, the setting will remove 'AD3' from the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs."
msgstr ""
"'PossibleNot' отображает список недозволенных Диалогов Активности. В примере "
"выше, настройка удаляет 'AD3' из списка заданных Диалогов Активности."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3498
msgid ""
"If both 'Possible' and 'PossibleNot' are specified, the list of configured "
"Activity Dialogs will first be filtered by 'Possible', leaving only 'AD1' "
"and 'AD3' in our example. Then 'PossibleNot' will be applied and filter out "
"'AD3', so that only 'AD1' remains and is shown as a possible Activity Dialog "
"that the user can use."
msgstr ""
"Если оба 'Possible' и 'PossibleNot' заданы, список заданных Диалогов "
"Активности сначала фильтруется используя 'Possible', оставляя 'AD1' и 'AD3' "
"в нашем примере. Затем применяется фильтр 'PossibleNot', который удаляет "
"'AD3', оставляя таким образом только 'AD1', как доступный пользователю для "
"использования Диалог Активности."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3505
msgid ""
"If multiple ACL rules match, the intersection of all matching rules will be "
"calculated to determine the possible Activity Dialogs. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Если множество правил ACL удовлетворяются, их пересечение будет вычислено "
"для определения доступных Диалогов Активности. Пример:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3511
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'001-ACL-Status'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Status => 'new',\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'002-ACL-Queue'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Queue => ['Raw']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD7'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'003-ACL-Priority'} = {\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        Ticket => {\n"
"            Priority => ['3 normal']\n"
"        }\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        ActivityDialog => ['AD3', 'AD4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3509
msgid ""
"Configured Activity Dialogs: 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', "
"'AD7'.  <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Заданные Диалоги Активности: 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', "
"'AD7'. <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3544
msgid ""
"If a process ticket has the state 'new', is in the 'Raw' queue and has a "
"priority '3 normal', then all three ACL rules will match."
msgstr ""
"Если заявка имеет состояние 'new', находится в очереди 'Raw' и имеет "
"приоритет '3 normal', то все три правила ACL будут удовлетворяться."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3548
msgid ""
"The first rule reduces the Activity Dialogs from 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD4', "
"'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7' to 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' and forbids 'AD4' "
"and 'AD5'."
msgstr ""
"Первое правило сокращает список Диалогов Активности с 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', "
"'AD4', 'AD5', 'AD6', 'AD7' до 'AD1', 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD6', 'AD7' и запрещает "
"'AD4' and 'AD5'.  "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3553
msgid ""
"The second rule will now further reduce the remaining Activity Dialogs.  In "
"our example, 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD7' will remain."
msgstr ""
"Второе правило еще сокращает список оставшихся Диалогов Активности. В нашем "
"примере, остаются 'AD2', 'AD3', 'AD7'."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3557
msgid ""
"Now the third rule will further reduce the list by 'PossibleNot'.  'AD3' is "
"removed from the list. 'AD4' is not removed, since it was not on the list in "
"the first place. At the end, 'AD2' and 'AD7' remain as possible Activity "
"Dialogs that the user can utilize."
msgstr ""
"Третье правило еще более сокращает список с помощью 'PossibleNot'. 'AD3' "
"удаляется из списка. 'AD4' не будет удален, т.к. он не на первом месте в "
"списке. И, наконец, 'AD2' и 'AD7' останутся, как доступные для выбора "
"пользователем Диалоги Активности."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3563
msgid ""
"It is also possible to limit the processes that can be displayed in the "
"\"New process ticket\" screen. The functionality is similar to limiting the "
"Activity Dialogs with one exception: The ACLs could only be based on Users."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3567
msgid "See examples below:"
msgstr "Смотрите примеры ниже:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3570
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'200-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            UserID => [2, 3],\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"       Process => ['P1', 'P2', 'P3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        Process => ['P4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'200-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            UserID => [2, 3],\n"
"        },\n"
"    },\n"
"    Possible => {\n"
"       Process => ['P1', 'P2', 'P3'],\n"
"    },\n"
"    PossibleNot => {\n"
"        Process => ['P4'],\n"
"    },\n"
"};\n"
"                    "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/customization/process-management.xml:3588
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$Self->{TicketAcl}->{'201-ACL-Process'} = {\n"
"    # match properties\n"
"    Properties => {\n"
"        User => {\n"
"            Group_rw => [ 'MyGroup' ],\n"
"        },\n"
