#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:9
msgid ""
"These instructions are for people upgrading OTRS from <emphasis>4</emphasis> "
"to <emphasis>5</emphasis> or from a <emphasis>5</emphasis> to a later "
"patchlevel release <emphasis>5</emphasis> and applies both for RPM and "
"source code (tarball) upgrades."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:15
msgid ""
"If you are running a lower version of OTRS you have to follow the upgrade "
"path to 4 first (1.1->1.2->1.3->2.0->2.1->2.2->2.3->2.4->3.0->3.1->3.2->3.3-"
">4)! You need to perform a full upgrade to every version in between, "
"including database changes and the upgrading Perl script."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:22
msgid ""
"Please note that if you upgrade from OTRS 2.2 or earlier, you have to take "
"<ulink url=\"http://bugs.otrs.org/show_bug.cgi?id=6798\">an extra step</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Помните, что если вы делаете обновление с OTRS 2.2 или более ранней, вы "
"должны выполнить <ulink url=\"http://bugs.otrs.org/show_bug.cgi?"
"id=6798\">дополнительный шаг</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:27
msgid ""
"Within a single minor version you can skip patch level releases if you want "
"to upgrade. For instance you can upgrade directly from OTRS 5 patchlevel 2 "
"to version 5 patchlevel 6. If you need to do such a \"patch level upgrade\", "
"you should skip steps 6, 10, 11, 14, 17 and 18."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><para>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:34
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to perform a test update on a separate testing "
"machine first."
msgstr ""
"Настоятельно рекомендуем выполнить сначала тестовое обновление в отдельной "
"тестовой среде."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:38
msgid "Step 1: Stop all relevant services"
msgstr "Шаг 1: Остановите все соответствующие службы"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:44
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> /etc/init.d/cron stop\n"
"shell> /etc/init.d/postfix stop\n"
"shell> /etc/init.d/apache stop\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> /etc/init.d/cron stop\n"
"shell> /etc/init.d/postfix stop\n"
"shell> /etc/init.d/apache stop\n"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:53
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> bin/Cron.sh stop\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Scheduler.pl -a stop\n"
msgstr ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> bin/Cron.sh stop\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Scheduler.pl -a stop\n"

#. type: CDATA
#: en/content/installation/upgrading.xml:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"shell> cd /opt/otrs/\n"
"shell> bin/Cron.sh stop\n"
"shell> bin/otrs.Daemon.pl stop\n"
msgstr ""

